# Branch : movement-system
#
# CREATED [CORE]: Movement Component
#
# - Built velocity-based movement system
# - Integrated with entity update loop
#
# Impact:
# - Foundation for all movement-related features
#
#
# ADDED [FEATURE]: Dash Mechanic
#
# - Added velocity multiplier for dash
# - Prepared cooldown hook integration
#
# Impact:
# - Enables fast-paced movement and combat mobility
#
#
# FIXED [BUG]: Movement Speed Overflow
#
# - Fixed issue where velocity exceeded max limit
# - Added clamping logic
#
# Impact:
# - Prevents unintended speed exploits
#
#
# Author: Yogesh-Kumar-Mallik-dev
# ========================================================